vala-lint
------------------------------------------
Small command line tool and library for checking Vala code files for code-style
errors. Based on the elementary Code-Style guidelines.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.11.2-1
  libgee0.8_2-0.20.1-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.54.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.31.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  meson-0.48.1-1
  ninja-1.8.2-2
  vala-0.38.8-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/elementary/vala-lint

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/elementary/vala-lint.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack vala-lint-0+git20180815-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./vala-lint-0+git20180815-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/vala-lint-0+git20180815-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vala-lint-0+git20180815-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(vala-lint)
  /usr/bin/cygvala-linter-1.0.dll
  /usr/bin/io.elementary.vala-lint.exe
  /usr/lib/libvala-linter-1.0.dll.a
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/vala-lint.README
  /usr/share/doc/vala-lint/README.md

------------------

